     A            AESUPL        40          COLHDG('SUPPLIER')
     A            AESHDT         8  0       COLHDG('SHIP DATE')
     A            AESHID        15          COLHDG('SHIP ID')
     A            AEORNO        10          COLHDG('ORDER NUMBER')
